questionsSolved.userSolution: SELECT FIRST_NAME,LAST_NAME,GENDER FROM patients WHERE GENDER='M';
SELECT FIRST_NAME FROM PATIENTS WHERE FIRST_NAME LIKE 'C%';
SELECT FIRST_NAME,LAST_NAME FROM PATIENTS WHERE ALLERGIES IS NULL;
SELECT FIRST_NAME,LAST_NAME FROM PATIENTS WHERE WEIGHT BETWEEN 100 AND 120;
SELECT CONCAT(FIRST_NAME,' ',LAST_NAME) AS FULL_NAME FROM PATIENTS;
SELECT P.FIRST_NAME,P.LAST_NAME,P1.PROVINCE_NAME FROM PATIENTS P LEFT JOIN PROVINCE_NAMES P1 ON P.PROVINCE_ID=P1.PROVINCE_ID;
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM PATIENTS WHERE YEAR(BIRTH_DATE)=2010;
